name: AMP-UP™ URETHANE
description:
AMP-UP™ URETHANE is a two component, high build acrylic aliphatic urethane with excellent color and gloss retention. Finish cures to a very tough, abrasive resistant film with exceptional exterior durability, chalk resistance, color stability and longterm gloss retention. AMP-UP™ URETHANE will
not degrade when exposed to the alkali on a construction site. Acids and detergents will not stain. This product was developed for use on
aluminum, as well as structural steel for both interior and exterior applications. Available in a full range of colors and a satin finish.
